This place now is a PU college. The building has elements of the old world. Must visit. The grand entrance,  porch,  lobby is all majestic . Wooden floors , grand arcs and big garden . The government acquired this may be under the land ceiling act. The nawabs lost ma y such buildings like other landlords.
Pls visit.
The current college authorities are mainting it well. Actually the ownership is with government cooperative society , who are involved in capacity building for banking societies .located in 1 st cross naryanpur near TV tower.
